ANF BRUSSELS Sunday , 26 Aug 2018 , 09:30 Peoples ' Democratic Congress-Europe -LRB- HDK-A -RRB- condemned in a written statement the attack ordered by the state against the Saturday Mothers in Istanbul on 25 August . For hours the Saturday Mothers and participants were subjected to violent attacks and repression , yet , as the statement stressed , they could carry out their action . - said the statement - This action has been held for 23 years . The HDK-A pointed out that in many European countries , as soon as the images of the police repression on Galatasaray went online , people held demonstrations to support the Saturday Mothers .